title: Verve Jazz Masters 46 - Ella Fitzgerald - The Jazz Sides (1995)
description:
Verve Jazz Masters 46 - Ella Fitzgerald - The Jazz Sides
Audio CD: August 22, 1995 
Original Release Date: August 22, 1995 
Label: Polygram Records 
Bitrate: 160-320 kbps

This is a great CD, that really does express the more flamboyant, and sexier side to Ella's incredible voice.  It's a treat from beginning to end, the first six tracks in my opinion are the best.  They do not compare to anything I have heard before.  This is what jazz is all about.  If you like Ella, you'll love this CD. ~ Jessica Tobias
